@ossified C1-OSS-01 HOOK_ON_LAST_LAYER_ONLY layers[-1] is the correct attach point; earlier layers still accumulating context, not persona-crystallized
@ossified C1-OSS-02 PERSONA_METADATA_NEVER_INJECTED persona_id travels in phi_vec._persona_id only; AN11(a) is guarded by function signature — do NOT add chat_template or system prompt to generate_with_phi
@ossified C1-OSS-03 HIVE_COLLEC_STRIDE_REQUIRED probe_phi_hive_collec is O(D·B²); stride max(1, D/32) keeps it tractable on D=5120 Qwen14B; without stride, single prompt phi computation blows past 60s
@ossified C1-OSS-04 CE_VIA_TEACHER_FORCING_FORWARD phi_holo_proxy = -log(CE) requires a second forward with labels=input_ids; measured at 0.46-1.33 CE on 3-prompt smoke → phi_holo_proxy ∈ [-13283, 7678] realistic envelope
